description:
How do you know whether you are experiencing true guilt or false guilt? The word of God helps us understand this topic, which can be very devastating when misunderstood. The Bible says, if we repent of and confess our sins and ask God for forgiveness, we are forgiven. This truth should liberate us from feeling guilty. If you suffer from chronic feelings of guilt, this intense teaching will help you identify false guilt and obtain freedom through God's word.
